## How to launch the project üöÄ
### Clone the project üìã
In ssh
```sh
git clone git@github.com:AestheticaLP/ArtistaFront.git
```

### Go the project folder üìÇ
```bash
cd ArtistaFront
```
### Install dependencies üê°
```sh
npm install
```

### Create a local.properties file :page_facing_up:
```sh
cp local.properties.example android/local.properties
```
Then change the link to your Sdk

### Build the app on your phone or emulator üì±
```sh
npm run android
```

### Run metro and reload ‚ìÇÔ∏è
```sh
npm start
```
```sh
Press r
```
